body.div: $10 9.$ who In fyrmyd that a comission scholde come downe that
was fyrst moysyon that serlys made to master london
at his fyrst comonig & london mayde hit sure & that
mayde them bolde & then he demandyd the names
of the onest of the temporallte & also of the spiritualte
of the temporallte was master moylle master baker
master thwates master boyes & diverse oder I can
not tell ther names & of the cherche master of
maydestone master of wye master parcus master
$i0.$ Indede i tolde master fogg of all that I knew & that I
harde that same talle: & so I dyd here hit in dede in
cryst cherche bot to tell hit as hit was tolde I can not
nor hoo tolde hit bot hit was spokon at atabyll
that my lordes grace scholde bottyd & sporyd Rede a
lector on the sacrament of the alter saying
hit was bot asemelytude & so lefte hit of Reavly
weche trobylde the herers hartes meche
